{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>特朗普在帖文稱「伊朗就是亂糟糟，他們都不知道如何簽無核協議。他們最好盡快聰明點！」</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126289269049004032458063.jpeg/42K-5w_B7gwZXFfSB63dEhAYPOJ2OXsYMLDkiTCw5Ik\" alt=\"特朗普社交網站帖文\"><figcaption>特朗普社交網站帖文</figcaption></figure><p>特朗普並在帖文上傳一張自己持槍的圖像，配上文字「不再當好好先生！」（No more Mr. Nice Guy!）。</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T15:24:02.696953+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":109,"images":1,"source":"HK01 國際","fallback":"none"}}